    "4: Compute the sum of selected entries for each row of X.",
    "5: Compute the rank of the target row among all rows in X to obtain x * rank.",
    "6: Normalize x * rank to lie in [0, 1]: x * rank ← x * rank /(N -1).",
    "7: for j ← 1 to ⌈m/2⌉ do ▷ Traverse the path from the root to the leaf.",
